  "page": 322,
  "statement_text": "The set C(ξ) is a normal subgroup of G1 .\n\nA proof of this result, and of Theorem 388G below, is given in Butcher (1972).\n  The D(ξ) condition is also represented by a subset of G1 , which is also\nknown to generate a normal subgroup.",
  "statement_latex": "\\begin{theorem}\nThe set $C(\\xi)$ is a normal subgroup of $G_1$.\n\nA proof of this result, and of Theorem~\\ref{thm:388G} below, is given in Butcher (1972).\nThe $D(\\xi)$ condition is also represented by a subset of $G_1$, which is also known to generate a normal subgroup.\n\\end{theorem}",
